# microservice specific routes

POST        /scope             @uk.gov.hmrc.controllers.ScopeController.createOrUpdateScope
GET         /scope             @uk.gov.hmrc.controllers.ScopeController.fetchScopes(keys ?= "*")
GET         /scope/:key        @uk.gov.hmrc.controllers.ScopeController.fetchScope(key)

POST        /scope/validate    @uk.gov.hmrc.controllers.ScopeController.validate